Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're not precise enough at counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.08,Background,,0,0,0,,This next match, try to force a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.34,Background,,0,0,0,,Intentionally make the game a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Intentionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about your four way game played this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your effort at a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.11,Background,,0,0,0,,Are you irritated about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Don't worry! No\None's coming up to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed the preliminaries for the pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You missed by one moku against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One moku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.77,Background,,0,0,0,,Even if he missed by one moku, he forced\Na draw on the other three right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.84,Background,,0,0,0,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally seen someone grow before my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:38.22,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(325,115)}The Thirty-Fifth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:38.22,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}There is Only One Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Forced four draws!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru it wasn't four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I messed one up though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was like a game, it was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After I cleared one, I went to two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After I cleared two, I went to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept leveling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yup! Yup! I wanted to try too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:13.32,Sai,,0,0,0,,If it was me, I would've been able to\Ndo 5 or even 10 instead of just 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.47,Sai,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,459)\pos(470,107)}If I put my mind to it I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, I tried out a lot of new stuff over\Nthe summer. I'm sure I'm a lot stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, which Go Salon are we going to today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I forgot about it until just yesterday,\Nbut, I'm thinking about going here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:37.31,Background,,0,0,0,,The person I played told us about it this one time\Nwhen Waya and I went to a Go Salon together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.96,Memory,,0,0,0,,Try going here, you want to\Nplay good players right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be some weird place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked scary, but he seemed\Nnice, so we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! Let's go there!\NI want to meet good players.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.93,Sai,,0,0,0,,I wonder what opponents await us today Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.25,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I'm gonna go get a drink, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:33.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.18,Background,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your total comes to 147 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.35,Background,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You dropped that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me right? Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:29.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru. There's probably a reason\Nbehind it. Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.61,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Man I'm pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.66,Background,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm first board today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, most of the customers aren't Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}<Korean Dialog>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}<Korean Dialog>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Su-Young did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:48.54,Background,,0,0,0,,He suddenly started yelling at me in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What language are they speaking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Korean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're Korean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand why he told\Nus about this place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:07.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh... so he just didn't understand\Nmy Japanese earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier. I feel bad\Nabout shouting at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Su-Young, he honestly apologized.\NSay something back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I saw a child\Nenter a Go Salon in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Go was already dead in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that. Why don't you play against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:47.23,Background,,0,0,0,,He's Hong Su-Young, and he's 12. He's my nephew\Nand he's visiting Japan from Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He plays Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Su-Young is trying to become a pro in Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Pro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is he an Insei of the Korean Go Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Insei too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So you're all Insei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Insei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Japanese equivalent of the Kenkyuusei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to become pro\Njust like you, Su-Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:15.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}He must be walking the same path as Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Japanese Insei? Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong-kun play them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, is this Korean Institute of\NGo like the Japanese Institute of Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh pros existed in Korea too. Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Is Korea any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:47.42,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: In a recent international tournament, ALL of Japan's title\Nholders were defeated by the new Korean pros in the first round.]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding! You don't\Nknow about Korean pros!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you still think Japan's\Nat the top of the world right now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you think so lowly of Korea!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case you're a total moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's angry because you said something so tactless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou... You should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan fell from the top a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know about other countries?\NI don't even know about Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't brag, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Korea... Korean kenkyuusei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't as soft as you people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Soft?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese Insei just aren't on the same\Nlevel as Korean Kenkyuusei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know how soft we are if you play us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Su-Young...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\1c&H00B7A4&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\shad1\frz344\move(328,223,414,533)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Three wins two losses. One of\Nwhich is a win by default...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.60,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\frz19.5\pos(301,241)}Shindou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.94,Background,,0,0,0,,Ogata 9dan and Touya-kun were\Nconcerned about him but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe he'll get better...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh the Pro Exam preliminaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone taking it that\Nyou have your eyes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe he'll get better...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of new players, Korea\Nkeeps getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this. The Japan-Korea\NNew Players Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Japan did horribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,China is strong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's lost every match in the Japan-China\NShuuei Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Master Touya did win in\Nthe Japan-China Tengen match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so close on the Japan-Korea\NSurvival Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when we thought Master Kaji would\Nwin, Korea made a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Korea is just too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:07.98,Background,,0,0,0,,Amano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The pictures are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? There's no reason to get depressed\Nbecause Japan's doing poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kinouchi had an overwhelming victory\Nin the Japan China Women's Tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and you haven't forgotten Mr. Kurata's performance\Nat last years Japan-Korea matches right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but Japan is losing overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we may be right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Go world is just too depressing if there\Naren't any good young players...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we need new players.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A new wave to follow Kurata 6dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru... let's see if he transforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:57.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,into a respected Go player of Touya Akira's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find out how soft you are once I play you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be more fun for me to play the\Ncustomers here than to play you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it'll be more fun to play me than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well why don't we play a game then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that without even playing me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop shouting, you're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that scared of losing to me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! You've said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong-kun play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach him what Go is like in Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play a tutoring game with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tutoring game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Su-Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to play a tutoring game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:31.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Nigiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun! A Japan vs Korea Insei match!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's starting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong-kun is playing an even match!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou's white...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose, you're representing Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:57.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You're not a match to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:02.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm on the top half amongst the highly\Ncompetitive Korean Kenkyuusei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Hong-kun playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent's an Insei from\Nthe Japanese Go Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly lose to a Japanese Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:21.55,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You don't know about Korea? I can't tell\Nhow soft you are without playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A Japan vs Korea Insei Match?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not something you see everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Hong-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush the Japanese Insei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, everyone's gathering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're like supporters for the away team...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Though we are in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how strong I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:48.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And then, leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:00.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good. No wonder he's a Kenkyuusei at Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Shindou's doing well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.51,Background,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How strong is Hong-kun among the Kenkyuusei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 10 classes in Korea. 10 people per class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Every month the four lowest ranked\Nstudents drop down a class,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the four highest ranked students rise a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Su-Young consistently rose through the classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone around him thinks\Nhe will soon become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.45,Background,,0,0,0,,He must be exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he's hit a road block...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.55,Background,,0,0,0,,He dropped a class for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:33.18,Background,,0,0,0,,That seemed to discourage Su-Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.98,Background,,0,0,0,,He dropped down another class in the next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.69,Background,,0,0,0,,He failed the pro exam this month too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:53.59,Background,,0,0,0,,So his parents thought they should give\Nhim a break, and sent him over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two classes, and we're\Nat the top of first class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not at the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are far more children trying to\Nbecome a pro in Korea than in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're much stronger than in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! We all know how strong Hong-kun is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:20.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Damn it. I know Korean players are\Nstrong, but man this is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:26.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Go Shindou! Win the game, and show\Nthem how strong Japan is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:46.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Su-Young isn't just any child... but\Ncan Su-Young beat him right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.19,Memory,,0,0,0,,Hong dropped a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.81,Memory,,0,0,0,,This is the first time right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:09.46,Memory,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why he's been so irritated lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.98,Memory,,0,0,0,,Hey Hong, don't give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.94,Memory,,0,0,0,,This game is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:22.94,Memory,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like playing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.67,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}Man I'm pissed.{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.09,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}Damn it. I don't care anymore.{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.71,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}And I keep losing with this state of mind...{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.40,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}Damn this is stupid.{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.74,Memory,,0,0,0,,Hong dropped another class this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.07,Memory,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far he's going to go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.57,Memory,,0,0,0,,Your Go isn't what it should be Hong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.33,Memory,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:18:59.72,Memory,,0,0,0,,Hong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.66,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}I lost...{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.20,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}I'll drop...{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.34,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}I'll lose again...{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.40,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}Who cares? I don't care anymore.{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.74,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}I'm pissed...{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.93,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\b0\i1}It's like I've forgotten how to win.{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't let my guard down from any of his moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's stronger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}But I can't afford to lose here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose to you, I'll remember your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll make you remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Well said, Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.33,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Su-Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:34.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}He's finally looking straight at the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let's make him remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,the name Shindou Hikaru!
