Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs20\fad(375,501)\1c&H0AB10F&\bord2\shad1\pos(55,286)}Shuusaku (Torajirou) was strong enough to be\Ncalled "The Godly Genius Child" at the age of 6
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuusaku had the child's name "Torajirou".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He learned Go from his mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and at six, no one in the area was a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs15.5\fad(417,501)\1c&H5043F3&\bord2\shad1\frz270\pos(577,188)}Written by Shuusaku at the age of 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to Edo at the age of 9, entered the\NHoninbou family, and studied under Jyouwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18.5\fad(334,501)\1c&H0AB40E&\fscx101\bord2\shad1\pos(319,367)}At age 9, he goes to Edo and studies under Honinbou Jyouwa
