Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:44.64,Op2English,,0,0,0,,Even then, I will find a deciding move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:53.64,Op2English,,0,0,0,,just as good as anyone else's, and take hold of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:57.19,Op2English,,0,0,0,,On this eye, this eye on yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.72,Op2English,,0,0,0,,everything will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:07.86,Op2English,,0,0,0,,I'll tell apart, just the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:11.23,Op2English,,0,0,0,,Even if the truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.94,Op2English,,0,0,0,,so harsh it's suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:18.44,Op2English,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to end
